snippet.title: King Rabbit - Puzzle Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: http://www.kingrabbit.co King Rabbit is an enjoyable way to improve your logic and creativity. Challenge yourself with puzzle and action levels. Get your creative juices flowing with the user-friendly level builder. The King Rabbit community is creating hundreds of new levels daily. Collect items, rabbits, and followers. Hop in!
